Hubert Harben https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hubert_Harben 0 Leonard Hubert S Harben (12 July 1878 – 24 August 1941) was an English stage and film actor. He was married to the actress Mary Jerrold and father of celebrity chef Philip Harben. Leonard_Hubert_S_Harben ( 12_July_1878 – 24_August_1941 ) was an_English_stage_and_film_actor .
